&lt;p>As of Saturday, 2 November 2024. I am embracing Hugo as my static website generator. It&amp;rsquo;s all started with Cyan Nyan
stream. Previously, I always wrote my website with
vanilla HTML/CSS but now im taking it easy with a pre-made template by &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack-starter" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>CaiJimmy Hugo Theme Starter&lt;/a>.
Very customizable with scss and there&amp;rsquo;s neat feature called shortcodes which you can see the embedded youtube video above.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Archives</title><link>https://nishimi-ya.github.io/archives/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nishimi-ya.github.io/archives/</guid><description/></item><item><title>About me</title><link>https://nishimi-ya.github.io/about-me/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nishimi-ya.github.io/about-me/</guid><description>&lt;div class="profiles">
